			"Data-driven" normalization & \cs{wateRmelon} & \cs{"wm.*"} \footnote{ * is a placeholder for the \cs{wateRmelon} normalization methods, e.g. "dasen", "nanet" etc.} & \cite{Pidsley2013} \\
